  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The effectiveness objective of this study is to evaluate whether 032-11 is non-inferior to
      Floseal as an adjunct to achieving haemostasis during surgical procedures involving cardiac
      and aortic thoracic surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
